text: Sabra taibaishanensis is a moth in the family Drepanidae. It was described by Chou and Xiang in 1987. It is found in China.Description of Sabra harpagula euroista Park, ssp. n. from Korea (Lepidoptera: Drepanidae) ==References== Category:Moths described in 1987 Category:Drepaninae Category:Moths of China
title: Sabra taibaishanensis
